0 0 20px 0;"><span>In each example, there&#8217;s a call: </span><strong>yo=
u can do big things</strong><span>. And there&#8217;s an admonition: </span=
><strong>you </strong><em><strong>must</strong></em><strong> do the biggest=
 thing you can do with your one shot.</strong><span>&#160;</span></p><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;">But what to work on? What&#8217;s the biggest thing you can do =
with your one shot?&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size:=
 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That&#8217;s a question only=
 you can answer, based on your talents and your own definition of &#8220;bi=
g.&#8221; There&#8217;s no right answer. You don&#8217;t have to cure cance=
r. I write a free newsletter.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>One way to=
 start thinking about it is by asking yourself what you would do if you had=
 all the resources in the world, because increasingly, you will.&#160;</str=
ong></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 2=
6px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Much is made of the fact that a common pers=
on today </span><em>consumes</em><span> products that kings and queens of o=
ld could never have imagined &#8211; iPhones, televisions, air conditioners=
, cars, medicine, airplanes.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64,=
 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>What&#=
8217;s less well-appreciated is that the common person today has access to =
tools with which to </span><em>create</em><span> that industrialists and CE=
Os of old couldn&#8217;t have fathomed, and that the toolkit is expanding e=
very single day.</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 1=
6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">With a big ambition in mind, i=
t&#8217;s like you have 8 billion people &#8211; and soon countless more di=
gital ones &#8211; working to provide you with exactly what you need to do =
the thing you were put on this earth to do. You have the world&#8217;s best=
 entrepreneurs, scientists, and researchers working to build things that ma=
ke your thing cheaper and more powerful. Their outputs become your inputs. =
What an unbelievable gift.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In this direct way - =
outputs becoming inputs &#8211; and in a less tangible but equally impactfu=
l way, ambition is contagious.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">SpaceX was the fo=
ur-minute mile for deep tech. It inspired (and trained) a generation of fou=
nders to go build things harder than they previously thought possible. That=
 generation is inspiring a new generation. Elon memed the current deep tech=
 explosion into existence, and the meme is spreading.&#160;</p><p style=3D"=
color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;"><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/7a449076-7abc-4953-8d43-a695=
796181e7?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU=
" rel style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">Optimis=
m shapes reality</a><span>, and it sets off a chain reaction. It bounces in=
to people, unleashing their energy and firing their own optimism into the n=
ext person to unleash more energy and more optimism.&#160;</span></p><p sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0=
 0 20px 0;">This reaction is underway now. You can feel it. There&#8217;s b=
een a vibe shift.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 1=
6px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I&#8217;m here to tell you tha=
t you can, even must, take part.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64=
); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">If you have som=
e time today, this weekend, or in the coming weeks, spend some of it thinki=
ng through what it is you want to do. Name it, give it a shape and weight.&=
#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">I&#8217;m not saying you need to awaken AGI or c=
ommercialize fusion. I write a free newsletter, who am I to tell you what b=
ig means for you?</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>As Isaac Asimov </span><a href=
=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/d2db0554-10d4-4266-90d8-ed8cbabb425f?j=3D=
eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel style=
=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">wrote</a><span> ha=
lf a century ago:&#160;</span></p><blockquote style=3D"border-left: 4px sol=
id #51b4e9; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64)=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px=
;"><em>Is the individual person wise enough to know what he or she can best=
 do? &#8212;Why not? Who else can know? And what can a person do best excep=
t that which he or she wants to do most?&#160;</em></p></blockquote><p styl=
e=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 =
0 20px 0;">What I can tell you is that you have the agency to do something =
bigger than you think possible. You can simply decide to do it, and the wor=
ld will bend itself to help you.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64=
); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>A couple =
of weeks ago, I spent time in San Francisco, a place where you can practica=
lly </span><em>see</em><span> ambition&#8217;s chain reaction with your own=
 eyes. I was talking to a founder about a challenge I was thinking through,=
 and after half a second of thought, she told me, essentially: &#8220;You n=
eed to go much bigger.&#8221;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);=
 font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">That sparked some=
thing in me, changed the way I approach the world. It gave me new confidenc=
e and raised my ambition. As I&#8217;ve pursued that ambition over the past=
 couple of weeks, everything I&#8217;ve written about in this piece started=
 happening. I&#8217;ve noticed the right tools materialize, pulled co-consp=
irators I have no business co-conspiring with into my orbit, and felt more =
energized than I have in a long time. We&#8217;ll see what happens, but it =
feels good.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">In the meantime, I&#8217;m passing t=
hat spark on to you.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Name your ambition. Make it=
 big, something worthy of your unique talents. Approach the chaos of change=
 with the clarity of purpose. Don&#8217;t let the machines take your job; p=
ut them to work for you.&#160;</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">You only live once, and=
 you get to live in the most magical time.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64=
, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">So tell me,=
 what is it you plan to do with your one wild and precious life?</p><div st=
